<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.1.5">
<l>cēppūṇṭa cāṭu citaṟit tiruṭineyk</l>
<l>kāppūṇṭu nantaṉ maṉaivi kaṭaitāmpāl</l>
<l>cōppūṇṭu tuḷḷit tuṭikkat tuṭikkavaṉ</l>
<l>ṟāppūṇṭā ṉappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟā</l>
<l rend="indent">ṉammaṉē yappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having shattered the cart that was yoked to an ox,</l>
<l>being bound for stealing ghee, being beaten with a churning rope</l>
<l>by Nanda’s wife and trembling so that [he was] very agitated that day,</l>
<l>he who was bound is making [the face of] a hobgoblin.</l>
<l>Oh! He is making [the face of] a hobgoblin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
